Today's episode for `justice-biotech-brief`:

**Pick:** Padcev + Keytruda — EC approves perioperative Nectin-4 ADC + PD-1 in cisplatin-ineligible muscle-invasive bladder cancer (June 24, 2026). First PD-1 inhibitor + ADC regimen ever authorized in a curative-intent setting. KEYNOTE-905 / EV-303 (n=595): pCR 57.1% vs 8.6%, EFS HR 0.40, OS HR 0.50.

**Files written** (SKIP_TTS stubs — orchestrator will handle TTS, R2, feed insert, commit):
