  - COMPASS pan-cancer ICI foundation model — medRxiv v4 update 2026-06-25, Zitnik lab Harvard (v1 was May 2025; v4 a minor revision, not a fresh story)
  - H&E ccRCC ICI predictor — bioRxiv v1 2026-06-25, UTSW + Roche/Genentech (Perny et al.); abstract-only, full body not rendered
  - Brepocitinib TYK2/JAK1 in dermatomyositis — medRxiv v1 2026-06-26, Mass General Brigham (Mangold et al.); n=5 pilot supporting NEJM/VALOR Phase 3; abstract-only
  - TLR3 agonist nanoparticle for cancer immunotherapy — bioRxiv v1 2026-06-25, Hammond lab MIT (Gomerdinger et al.); mouse-only
